name: Mas Marami Tayo
description:
“Mas Marami Tayo”
Acrylic on Canvas
Size: 24” x 36”

Artists or not—we can make a difference. Every election reminds us that regardless who you are or where you came from; your voice has power and it matters. Our country needs YOU—our country needs every Filipinos to take part in rebuilding our nation in the wake of a crisis.

We need to unite, rise up, engage, and make our voices be heard. The future we envision for us and the future generations depends on the choices we make. Together, through our collective efforts, we can continue moving, towards a brighter tomorrow. Together, we can change the course of our history.
